<blockquote class="western" style="border: medium; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-align: center;">
<span face="fkGroteskNeue, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji, Hiragino Sans, PingFang SC, Apple SD Gothic Neo, Yu Gothic, Microsoft YaHei, Microsoft JhengHei, Meiryo"><span style="font-size: small;"><i><b>The
