	<li><p class="western" style="border: medium; letter-spacing: normal; margin-bottom: 0cm; padding: 0cm; text-align: center;">
	<span face="fkGroteskNeue, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji, Hiragino Sans, PingFang SC, Apple SD Gothic Neo, Yu Gothic, Microsoft YaHei, Microsoft JhengHei, Meiryo"><span style="font-size: small;"><b>At
	the highest layer sit¬†<span style="border: medium; display: inline-block; padding: 0cm;">global
	constraints and information structures</span>: symmetries,
	conservation principles, boundary conditions, and what counts as
